Sentencas: Industrial-sized planar anode-supported SOFC cells with a cell dimension of 15 x 15 x 0.1 cm and an active area of 13 x 13 cm(2) are fabricated through a processing route of tape casting-screen printing-cofiring.
Titulo: Electrochemical performance and thermal cyclicability of industrial-sized anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Electrochemical performance and thermal cyclicability of the cell are evaluated in a single cell stack at 750 degrees C with H-2 as the fuel and air as the oxidant.
Titulo: Electrochemical performance and thermal cyclicability of industrial-sized anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: With a gas flow rate of 3 L min(-1), the initial open circuit voltage (OCV) is 1164 mV, and the stack demonstrates a power density of 380 mW cm(-2) at 473 mA
Titulo: Electrochemical performance and thermal cyclicability of industrial-sized anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells

Titulo: Electrochemical performance and thermal cyclicability of industrial-sized anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: After three thermal cycles, the reduction of the stack output voltage is around 5%, and the OCV is maintained at a level above 1145 mV. Based on the obtained results, issues related to stack performance, such as cell quality, contact resistance and sealing, are discussed.
Titulo: Electrochemical performance and thermal cyclicability of industrial-sized anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells
